NIBBLER PROJECT
===============

How to run the project ?
------------------------

    $> make re
    $> ./nibbler [WIDTH] [HEIGHT] lib_nibbler_[LIB].so

What is it ?
------------

     - Fully functionnal snake game with 3 graphic libraries

What are the details ?
----------------------

     - Press the arrow keys to move the snake
     - Eat randomly placed apples to grow
     - Avoid randomly placed obstacles
     - Your score is printed on the top of the screen
     - Press the space bar for a speed boost
     - The speed increases the longer the game goes
     - Press escape to end the game
